        "title": "feat: add xAI OAuth web search and provider timeouts",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Add plugin-authored `defaultTimeoutMs` support for image, video, and speech provider contracts, with caller/config timeouts taking precedence over provider defaults.\n- Set xAI image and video generation defaults to 600 seconds for long-running generation calls.\n- Let Grok `web_search` reuse xAI OAuth auth profiles with API-key fallback, including refresh/retry handling for stale OAuth credentials.\n- Add Grok Build catalog aliases and update the related provider/tool docs.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `pnpm tsgo:core`\n- `pnpm tsgo:extensions`\n- `pnpm tsgo:core:test`\n- `pnpm tsgo:extensions:test`\n- `pnpm test src/flows/search-setup.test.ts extensions/xai/web-search.test.ts`\n- Focused Vitest via repo wrapper for `src/image-generation/runtime.test.ts`, `src/video-generation/runtime.test.ts`, `extensions/speech-core/src/tts.test.ts`, `extensions/xai/image-generation-provider.test.ts`, `extensions/xai/video-generation-provider.test.ts` (5 files, 85 tests)\n- `pnpm format:docs:check`\n- `pnpm format:check -- src/flows/search-setup.test.ts extensions/xai/web-search.test.ts`\n- `git diff --check -- src/flows/search-setup.test.ts extensions/xai/web-search.test.ts`\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nBehavior addressed: Plugins can provide default operation timeouts for long-running media providers, xAI image/video defaults are 600 seconds, and Grok web_search can use xAI OAuth with API-key fallback.\n\nReal environment tested: Local OpenClaw source checkout on macOS using repo wrappers and focused Vitest/type lanes.\n\nExact steps or command run after this patch: `pnpm tsgo:core`, `pnpm tsgo:extensions`, `pnpm tsgo:core:test`, `pnpm tsgo:extensions:test`, `pnpm test src/flows/search-setup.test.ts extensions/xai/web-search.test.ts`, focused media-provider Vitest run, docs format check, scoped format check, and scoped diff whitespace check.\n\nEvidence after fix: Type lanes passed; focused search setup/web-search tests passed in 2 Vitest shards with 51 tests; focused media-provider tests passed with 5 files and 85 tests.\n\nObserved result after fix: Timeout precedence and xAI 600-second defaults are covered by focused tests; Grok web_search OAuth selection, refresh retry, and API-key fallback are covered by focused tests.\n\nWhat was not tested: Live external xAI image, video, or web_search API calls were not run.\n",
